<li><a href="/wiki/Martini_Shot" title="Martini Shot">Martini Shot</a> - a <a href="/wiki/Film_industry" title="Film industry">film industry</a> <a href="/wiki/Slang" title="Slang">slang</a> term for the last <a href="/wiki/Shot_(filming)" title="Shot (filming)" class="mw-redirect">shot</a> of the day, because "the next shot is out of a glass".</li>
</ul>
